data.description: This is a well-maintained 4 bedroom/1 bath home that sits on a gently sloping lot within the rural community of Middlebourne in east-central Ohio. Sitting just off I-70, this property provides a commute to Cambridge or St. Clairsville within 20 minutes. The sale will include an electric range, refrigerator, wood burner, and the washer and dryer. There are 3 outbuildings on the property to provide you with plenty of storage space. There is a spring house on the property, and the property also boasts a private well that is reported to pump 8 gallons of water a minute. A woodburning stove provides a second source of heat to the home and will keep you cozy during the winter in addition to the forced air, fuel oil furnace. Mineral rights are not owned so do not transfer. Showings are by appointment only.
